videos.description: Texas guard Jase Febres gets open from beyond the arc and banks his shot off the backboard to score the game's first points.
videos.headline: Longhorns bank in 3 to open game

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young drives to the hoop but has his layup swatted off the glass by Texas' Mohamed Bamba.
videos.headline: Bamba rejects Young at the rim

videos.description: Texas' Mohamed Bamba gets the ball off the pick-and-roll then elevates to slam home a powerful one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Bamba flushes vicious tomahawk slam

videos.description: Longhorns guard Kerwin Roach II comes off a screen and rises up for an emphatic slam.
videos.headline: Texas' Roach throws down the hammer

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young drives to the hoop and uses a double-clutch lay-in to evade the defender and score.
videos.headline: Young sinks acrobatic layup

videos.description: With time winding down in the first half, Oklahoma's Trae Young dishes to Kameron McGusty, who knocks down a contested 3 as the buzzer sounds.
videos.headline: Sooners' triple beats halftime buzzer

videos.description: With both the Jets and the Giants looking for a QB in the NFL draft, Baker Mayfield says he would "love" to play in New York and has even heard a nickname: "Broadway Baker."
videos.headline: New York hype earns Mayfield new nickname

tracking.trackingName: COM_NFL Interview (New York hype earns Mayfield new nickname) 2018/02/17 ESHEET

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young pulls up from well beyond the arc to sink his first 3-pointer of the game.
videos.headline: Young drills deep 3-ball

videos.description: Texas' Dylan Osetkowski blocks a shot and keeps the ball alive, setting up a Jacob Young transition score.
videos.headline: Longhorns turn defense into offense

videos.description: Oklahoma's Rashard Odomes drives to the hoop and has his shot blocked off the backboard by Texas' Mohamed Bamba.
videos.headline: Bamba swats shot off glass

videos.description: Oklahoma's Trae Young shows off a quick release on an off-the-dribble 3 from NBA-range.
videos.headline: Young drains pull-up triple

videos.description: Texas forward Dylan Osetkowski crashes the offensive glass,  grabbing a board before rising up for the dunk.
videos.headline: Texas' Osetkowski scores with putback slam

videos.description: After racking up 10 points, 18 boards and 4 blocks in a win over Oklahoma, Mohamed Bamba talks about Texas' goals for the rest of the season.
videos.headline: Bamba: 'We want to play in the tournament'

videos.description: Dick Vitale and Bob Wischusen break down the Longhorns' win over the Sooners, saying Trae Young must fix his shooting woes for Oklahoma to be successful.
videos.headline: Oklahoma's struggles continue against Texas

videos.description: Trae Young finishes with 26 points but is only 7-of-21 from the field in the Sooners' 77-66 loss to the Longhorns.
videos.headline: Young's 26 can't prevent Oklahoma's fifth straight loss

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Young's 26 can't prevent Oklahoma's fifth straight loss) 2018/2/17 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.description: Trae Young scores 26 points but Mohamed Bamba counters with 10 points and 18 rebounds in the Longhorns' 77-66 victory over the Sooners.
videos.headline: Texas hands Oklahoma fifth straight loss
